actionListener

Class StartUpMenuActionListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • actionListener.StartUpMenuActionListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class StartUpMenuActionListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    This class StartUpMenuActionListener is the event controller of the class StartUpView.

    This class controls all the actions performed by the different JComponents added in the layout of the Start up view class. It implements an ActionListener
